snippet.title: Dota 2 Reborn: Custom Games Are Here (English)
snippet.description:
Learn more about the Dota 2 Reborn update here: http://www.dota2.com/reborn/

Custom Games are new experiences that are created by the community, and playable within Dota 2. These games can be anything from a grand brawl between ten Invokers, to a story-driven dungeon adventure, to something creative that no one has seen before.

Also viewable in
Chinese: http://youtu.be/Za2uL3mcfbg
Russian: http://youtu.be/qS_OxehC6eo
Korean: http://youtu.be/Ihx8x-Rn8vk
